<div class='noset'>
  전체 단어 수 : <b><%=@word_cnt%>개</b> ☆ 
  현재 이미지 없는거 : <b style='color:red;'><%=@picture_cnt%>개</b> ☆ 
  검토완료 : <b style='color:red;'><%=@confirm_cnt%>개</b>/<%=@picture_cnt%>개<br/><br/>
  <b>Click !! <span id='origin' class='pointer'>원래대로</span> ■ 
  <span id='noimage' class='pointer'>안한거 앞으로 끌고 오기</span> ■ 
  <span id='confirm' class='pointer'>검토하기 GoGo~</span> ■
  <span id='confirm_finished' class='pointer'>검토 완료된 거</span> ■ 
  <input type='text' name='search' class='search'> <input type='button' id='search_word' value='Search' class='btn' style='margin-bottom:9px;'></b>
</div>
<table class="table table-hover">
  <tr>
    <th>ID</th>
    <th>Name</th>
    <th>Mean</th>
    <th>phonetics</th>
    <th>ko_exam</th>
    <th>en_exam</th>
    <th>is_picture</th>
    <th></th>
    <th></th>
  </tr>
  <% for word in @words %>
    <tr>
      <td><%= word.id %></td>
      <td><%= word.name %></td>
      <td><%= word.mean %></td>
      <td><%= word.phonetics %></td>
      <td><%= word.example_ko %></td>
      <td><%= word.example_en %></td>
      <td><%= 'O' if word.picture == 1 %></td>
      <td><%= link_to "Edit", edit_admin_word_path(word, :before_page => @page, :is_align => @align), :class => 'btn btn-warning' %></td>
      <td><% link_to "Destroy", [:admin, word], :data => { confirm: 'Text' }, :method => :delete, :class=>'btn btn-danger' %></td>
    </tr>
  <% end %>
</table>
<%= paginate(@words) %>
